Code Tester Requirements:
Python Version: >=3.6 (Preferably 3.9+ for better compatibility)
Pygments — for syntax highlighting

OS: Windows Only
Make sure to run in admin rights for the best results

System-Level Requirements (for compilers/interpreters)
Depending on which languages you're running, the following must be installed and added to your system's PATH:

Language	Required Software
Python	Python (obviously)
Java	JDK (Java Development Kit)
C / C++	GCC (MinGW for Windows)
JavaScript	Node.js
Go	Golang compiler (go)
Rust	Rust toolchain (rustc, cargo)
⚠️ If you don’t add these to the system PATH, subprocess calls will fail or throw “command not found” errors. ⚠️
